text: Jump Up! is the sixteenth studio album by Elton John and was released on 9 April 1982 by Geffen Records. It went to number 1 in New Zealand, number 3 in Australia and Norway, number 13 in the United Kingdom, number 15 in Sweden, number 17 in the United States and number 19 in Canada. == Track listing == Category:1982 albums Category:Elton John albums
title: Jump Up! (Elton John album)
